wikipedia_page.main: Grace Fenton Garner (born 19 June 1997) is an English former professional racing cyclist, who rode professionally between 2016 and 2020, for the Podium Ambition Pro Cycling, Wiggle High5, Hitec Products–Birk Sport and CAMS–Tifosi teams. Her older sister Lucy van der Haar also competed professionally in cycling, before also retiring in 2020.
